ГўВЂВњThe Land Bank of the Philippines shall manage the credit facility funded out of the Fund and shall determine the eligibility requirements and set the required loan security or collateral and reasonable interest for the loan. For this purpose, the Land Bank is hereby authorized to charge a management fee from the Fund;

